Patch Set 18:

To reproduce the bug:
- touch $MOUNT/file.{0..5}
- lhsmtool_posix --hsm-root /dev/shm $MOUNT &
- lfs hsm_archive $MOUNT/file.{0..5}
- lfs hsm_release $MOUNT/file.{0..5}
- kill -STOP %1
- lfs hsm_restore $MOUNT/file.{0..5}
- kill -TERM %1
- kill -CONT %1 # Requests get canceled
- lhsmtool_posix --hsm-root /dev/shm $MOUNT &
- cat $MOUNT/file.0 # Gets stuck
